item.content:encoded:
I welcome everyone on my personal blog. I am a Fullstack Software Engineer, so the posts will be mainly about Software Development and related topics.

When there is no new blog post in the mean time, also have a look at my Wiki. It contains things that I often look up and notes about certain technologies and everything else that does not fit in a blog post. See it like a wikipedia for Fullstack Software Engineers.
